WEBVTT

00:07:28.949 --> 00:07:31.564
approximately one percent
of the population

00:07:31.588 --> 00:07:35.164
is diagnosed with autism
spectrum disorder.

00:07:35.188 --> 00:07:36.988
And this number is growing.

00:07:37.760 --> 00:07:40.852
However, we are still a big minority.

00:07:41.217 --> 00:07:44.876
And there's still lots of people
that do not see us as equals

00:07:44.900 --> 00:07:46.209
to other people.

00:07:48.368 --> 00:07:50.122
This is my family.

00:07:50.784 --> 00:07:53.580
And in my family,

00:07:53.604 --> 00:07:57.823
there is one other person
who is also autistic.

00:07:58.411 --> 00:07:59.688
My mother.

00:07:59.712 --> 00:08:03.348
Yes, adult women can also be autistic.